dagify(c ~ a,
       f ~ c,
       a ~ d,
       c ~ d,
       f ~ d,
       d ~ b + g,
       b ~ e) |>
  ggdag_equivalent_dags(node_size = 10) +
  theme_dag()

dagify(Y ~ X) |>
  ggdag_equivalent_dags() +
  theme_void()

three_var_coords <- read.csv(text = "name,x,y
                             treat,0,0
                             out,1,0
                             med,0.5,0.5")
three_var_coords
dagify(out   ~ med + treat,
       med   ~ treat,
       exposure = "treat", outcome = "out", coords = three_var_coords) |>
  #ggdag() |>
  ggdag_equivalent_dags() +
